trans-unit.source: Provides an extension point that can access member characteristics of a XAML member through techniques other than reflection.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller ett tillägg som kan komma åt medlemmen egenskaper för en medlem i XAML med metoder än reflektion.

trans-unit.source: The purpose of XamlMemberInvoker is to enable an extensible XAML type system, schema, and a working run time that does not rely as fully on CLR features such as CLR attributes, reflection information through <xref:System.Type> and <xref:System.Reflection.MemberInfo>, and so on.
trans-unit.target: Syftet med XamlMemberInvoker är att aktivera en utökningsbar XAML-typsystemet, schema och en fungerande körningstiden som inte är beroende som fullständigt CLR-funktioner, till exempel CLR-attribut, reflektion information via <xref:System.Type>och <xref:System.Reflection.MemberInfo>och så vidare.</xref:System.Reflection.MemberInfo> </xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Subclasses of XamlMemberInvoker are used as input parameters for the alternate constructors of XAML schema classes such as <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>.
trans-unit.target: Underklasser för XamlMemberInvoker används som indataparametrar för alternativa konstruktorerna i XAML-schemaklasser, till exempel <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>.</xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>

trans-unit.source: You subclass <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember> and pass the XamlMemberInvoker through to the base constructor.
trans-unit.target: Du underklass <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>och skickar XamlMemberInvoker via till konstruktorn grundläggande.</xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>

trans-unit.source: Along with defining a XamlMemberInvoker for the constructor, you must also provide overrides for at least some of the `Lookup` methods of <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>.
trans-unit.target: Tillsammans med definierar en XamlMemberInvoker för konstruktorn måste du även ange åsidosättningar för minst några av de `Lookup` metoder av <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>.</xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>

trans-unit.source: XamlMemberInvoker has a default implementation.
trans-unit.target: XamlMemberInvoker har en standardimplementering.

trans-unit.source: The default implementation follows a similar model to the default implementation of XAML schema types <xref:System.Xaml.XamlType> and <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>: the CLR type system is used for instantiation, values and lookups, including using CLR attributes, <xref:System.Type> and <xref:System.Reflection.MemberInfo>, and so on.
trans-unit.target: Standardimplementering följer en liknande modell till standardimplementering av XAML schematyper <xref:System.Xaml.XamlType>och <xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember>: CLR-typsystemet används för instansiering, värden och sökningar, inklusive användning av CLR-attribut, <xref:System.Type>och <xref:System.Reflection.MemberInfo>och så vidare.</xref:System.Reflection.MemberInfo> </xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Xaml.XamlMember> </xref:System.Xaml.XamlType>

trans-unit.source: XamlMemberInvoker provides methods for basic get and set operations (<xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.GetValue%2A>; <xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.SetValue%2A>).
trans-unit.target: XamlMemberInvoker innehåller metoder för grundläggande get och set-åtgärder (<xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.GetValue%2A>; <xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.SetValue%2A>).</xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.SetValue%2A></xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.GetValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: It also provides the properties <xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.UnderlyingGetter%2A> and <xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.UnderlyingSetter%2A>, but these are not virtual.
trans-unit.target: Det ger också egenskaperna <xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.UnderlyingGetter%2A>och <xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.UnderlyingSetter%2A>, men dessa är inte virtuell.</xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.UnderlyingSetter%2A> </xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.UnderlyingGetter%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > It may be possible to obtain a XamlMemberInvoker value that represents a XAML directive, which is implemented as a private class in the System.Xaml implementation.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Kan det vara möjligt att få ett XamlMemberInvoker-värde som representerar ett XAML-direktiv som implementeras som en privat klass i System.Xaml implementeringen.

trans-unit.source: If you attempt to call <xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.GetValue%2A> or <xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.SetValue%2A> on this invoker, an exception is thrown.
trans-unit.target: Om du försöker anropa <xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.GetValue%2A>eller <xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.SetValue%2A>på den här anropar ett undantag.</xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.SetValue%2A> </xref:System.Xaml.Schema.XamlMemberInvoker.GetValue%2A>
